2010-05-19 Alexander Nitsch <nitscha@cs.tu-berlin.de>
	* src/modules/flt_postingassistant.c: The posting assistant will
		now skip checks for upper/lower case in the subject if a
		follow-up posting did not change the subject.

2010-03-25 Alexander Nitsch <nitscha@cs.tu-berlin.de>
	* cmake/modules/FindICU.cmake: Made CMake stop if ICU lib cannot
		be found.
	* cmake/modules/FindPerlLibs.cmake: Added Debian's default scheme
		to list of possible include paths for Perl header file.
	* CMakeLists.txt: Explicitly specified the project's language
		so CMake will not complain about a missing C++ compiler that
		is not needed anyway.

